>   I am using Evo 1.4.5, and cannot find a setting to ensure
> me messages will wrap at 72 characters, or any other number
> for that matter. How can I set this?

Use paragraph style "Normal" (which should be default for composing
text/plain messages anyway) and lines will break at 72 chars.

Quoted lines are set to "Preformat" by default, which will not wrap at
all.


As Jeff already said: The setting of 72 chars is hard coded and cannot
be customized without recompiling...

....guenther


